Hey Dungeoneers,
The Dark Dungeons DVD is almost ready to go to print!  Everyone should have filled out and returned their survey which asked how you wanted your name to appear on the DVD.  Those answers have been put in a spreadsheet and are about to be locked in. 
If you haven't sent in your survey yet then you need to;

Hi Dungeoneers!

The final Dark Dungeons trailer can be found on our webpage;
http://darkdungeonsthemovie.com/
As well linked to in this article in Wired;

And here it is, the moment you have been waiting for, the very first trailer for DARK DUNGEONS THE MOVIE;
http://on.fb.me/1cSc4gj 
Please share this far and wide!  It's really hard to get news about small projects like this out, so we absolutly depend upon the support of fans like you to spread the word.  If you would take five seconds to share this link
